These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, whist, poker, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, cycling, sailing, skateboarding
1. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person playing whist##1
6. the person playing poker is the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Game      | chess  | monopoly | whist  | poker |
| Sport   | sailing | skateboarding      | lacrosse | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
City: new-york, prague, nizza, miami
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, family, drama, zombie
1. the person traveling to prague is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching zombie movies##2
2. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| City   | miami | nizza | prague   | new-york |
| Movie-Genre           | drama      | spy    | family | zombie      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, magic-tricks, singing, fishing
1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
6. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage        | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | lemonade     | water |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks  | fishing   | singing | baking    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, ebony, turquise, lilac
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, iris, daisy, azalea
1. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaisy##5
3. the person who likes grey is between the person who growsazalea and the person who growsiris##2
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
5. the person who growsazalea is the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Color         | turquise | grey | ebony | lilac |
| Flower   | azalea   | daisy     | iris    | balloon-flower       |

