.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, teacher, coach, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, june, august
1. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
2. the social-worker is on the left or right of the coach##3
3. the coach is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the teacher##3
6. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Job          | coach | social-worker   | bartender   | teacher    |
| Birthday   | february  | august | may | june |

