.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, ivory, coral, turquise
4 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, goat, frog
1. the person who likes turquise is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
3. the owner of the frog is between the person who likes turquise and the owner of the goat##2
4. the person who likes coral is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Color           | white | ivory | turquise | coral |
| Pet   | goat        | frog     | hamster       | horse   |

