.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, writing, photography, board-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, bike, boat
1. the person driving the van is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person driving the bike##2
3. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | writing | gardening  | photography  | board-games   |
| Transport           | boat  | jet-ski | bike | van |

