.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, scientific, disaster, zombie
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, chestnut, black, purple
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | zombie | disaster     | crime   |
| Color    | purple | chestnut  | black | red |

