.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, colombian, mexican, british
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, van, snowmobile, ship
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the british##1
3. the dutch is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
5. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
6. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | dutch | mexican | british   | colombian |
| Transport       | motorbike       | snowmobile   | ship | van |

