.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose, lily, balloon-flower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, punk, ambient, trance
1. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
2. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
3. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
4. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
5. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Flower   | rose | lily       | zinnia   | balloon-flower        |
| Music-Genre      | punk  | trance | d&b | ambient |

