.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, architect, scientist, project-manager
There are 4 different nationalities: french, american, mexican, russian
1. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
2. the mexican is the scientist##1
3. the american is on the left of the architect##1
4. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
5. the american is somewhere to the left of the french##5
6. the french is on the left or right of the american##3
7. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the french##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | lawyer | architect   | scientist | project-manager     |
| Nationality   | american     | french | mexican  | russian |

