.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, snake, horse, pony
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, australian, indian, french
1. the french is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the french is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
4. the owner of the bird is the indian##1
5. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
6. the australian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Pet   | bird | horse        | pony        | snake |
| Nationality         | indian  | french | nigerian | australian |

