The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower, begonia, daffodil
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person playing chess##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person playing bridge is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Game         | billiard | bridge | chess | scrabble |
| Flower   | dahlia     | daffodil  | balloon-flower  | begonia    |

