.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, aquamarine, red, ivory
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, reading, card-games, board-games
1. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
2. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who likes red##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Color   | ivory  | purple | aquamarine | red |
| Hobby   | card-games | puzzles | reading   | board-games  |

