.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, lemonade, juice
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, scrabble, backgammon
1. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
5. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Beverage   | coffee | lemonade  | juice      | hot-chocolate |
| Game     | scrabble    | backgammon | poker | mah-jongg   |

