.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, golf, climbing, swimming
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, azalea, lily, aconite
1. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
4. the person who growstulip is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
6. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who growsazalea##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Sport      | tennis   | climbing  | golf      | swimming       |
| Flower   | lily | aconite | azalea | tulip |

