2. the person drinking tea is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | juice     | sprite | coffee | tea |
| Hobby     | rock-climbing | drawing    | photography    | board-games |

