.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, sports, drama, zombie
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, siglo, dannemann, swisher
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the swisher-smoker##5
3. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
4. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the siglo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Movie-Genre      | drama     | zombie | adventure     | sports |
| Cigar   | dannemann | swisher  | davidoff | siglo        |

