3. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
5. the indian is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality         | egyptian   | indian   | brazilian       | argentine   |
| Sport   | lacrosse | ice-hockey | climbing | cycling |

