.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, turtle, goldfish, goat
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, chestnut, light-blue, fuchsia
1. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person who likes chestnut##5
5. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##5
6. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the goat and the person who likes white##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Pet        | turtle     | goat | snake | goldfish |
| Color   | light-blue | fuchsia | chestnut      | white        |

 